The Chronicle Mthabisi Tshuma, Showbiz Reporter PREPARATIONS are at an advanced stage for gospel sensation Janet Manyowa’s debut live performance in Bulawayo with the artiste expected to arrive in the city today. The show taking place at the ZITF Hall 3 on Saturday has been dubbed “In the City of Kings and Queens Wanqoba Concert with Janet Manyowa”. <img class="wp-image-622828 size-full" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/06/Stage-being-erected-for-Janet-Manyowa-concert.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/06/Stage-being-erected-for-Janet-Manyowa-concert.jpg 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/06/Stage-being-erected-for-Janet-Manyowa-concert-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> Stage being erected for Janet Manyowa concert It will be headlined by talented musicians who include Mai Mwamuka, Snowy, Vocal Ex, Harvest House Music Choir, Wenyasha, Takesure Zamar, Ntokozo Mbambo and Nomthie Sibisi. <img class="alignnone wp-image-622834 size-full" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/06/Janet-234.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/06/Janet-234.jpg 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/06/Janet-234-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> Said Janet Manyowa: “Preparations for the event are going on well as we’re well on schedule for the Saturday event. As the city was voted for in a poll where we asked our fans where to perform, we expect fireworks. The headline acts will certainly bring their A-game.” <img class="wp-image-622831 size-full" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/06/Pastor-G.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/06/Pastor-G.jpg 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/06/Pastor-G-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> Pastor G She said there will be guest appearances from Mike Mahendere and Pastor G among others with Pastor G and Wenyasha expected in the city today. Bonnie Deuschle is expected to arrive tomorrow with the rest arriving on Saturday. <img class="wp-image-622840 size-full" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/06/Bonnie.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/06/Bonnie.jpg 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/06/Bonnie-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> Bonnie Attendees are expected to be given another amazing gospel experience after the success of Everton Mlalazi and Pastor Barak Live concerts in the city recently. – @mthabisi_mthire      